parameters:
Papa! Look, look~! I'm going to become a magical
girl too~

Oh, wow~ That's amazing~ But why do you want to
become a magical girl?

Because you see, magical girl Konoha is really
strong! If I become strong too, I can save Mama!

I see, I see~ Then if Yayori becomes a magical
girl... Magical Girl Mili! That's it!

Yeah! But, isn't it a bit too short? Maybe it
would be better to have Kurashima Yumisato for the
full name?

I see~ Magical Girl Kurashima Mili! Are you going
to become that? Isn't it too long?
That's not true~! Take this magical attack~!
Ouch, ouch, ouch! That's not magic, you know~
Ugh... Mama... she became a... star...

Why... was Yari a bad child...? Because she wasn't
a magical girl...?

Yumisato did nothing wrong... Nothing...
Nothing...
I don't want to... I can't meet Mama...
Ah, Yayori! Where are you going...!

(If I become a magical girl... I could heal
Mama...)

(If I become a magical girl like Konoha...
surely...)

What is this...? Did I have a shiny book like
this?

Maybe I should give it a read... Who knows, I
might become a magical girl♪

Konoha and Rudia were able to safely return to
their hometown. Both of them returned to their
original bodies and only had to return to Gardis.

All those who were reincarnated into Grimoire Land
have returned to their original world. With the
disappearance of demons from Grimoire Land, there
will no longer be anyone reincarnating into this
world.

Lolimon, magical beasts, and humans... Grimoire
Land has become a peaceful world, and their story
will be forever woven.
